Human-Machine Consensus: By holding the coin, the recipient’s bio-electric field "tags" the anchor.
The Monitoring: Robotics in the future maintain a "Quantum Zeno" lock on the coin, ensuring the recipient remains in a trackable reality branch, effectively "pinning" their existence across spacetime.
